Hollis Ave., south side, between 198th and 199th Streets,

Hollis Ave., north side, between 198th and 200th Sts., showing in a set of two views, the Oldfield Hendrickson house. IIt was occupied by the Hendrickson family from 1860 to 1908, when Walter Horn bought
it in 1908. He still occupied it in 1923.
May 1923.
Views 1 and 2.
